  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_chem-354334.pdf_20_3",
    "text": "We will explore a more detailed analysis of these orbital interactions in the next chapter. For now, we can summarize the most common outcomes in the table below. We should note that there is one important cycloaddition, the [2+2] thermal reaction of ketenes that does not conform to this generalized analysis.",
